# Local/private artifacts
# Scoped to folders rather than file types so you can intentionally commit
# reference materials (e.g. a saved job posting PDF) when useful.
# Keep the blank template but exclude any filled-in resume files
resume/*
!resume/_template.md
private/

# Personal working notes
notes.md

# OS/editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
